360 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_SAMPLER_CUBE:
361 return 69;
362 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_SAMPLER_CUBE_MAP_ARRAY:
363 return 70;
364 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_SAMPLER_BUFFER:
365 return 71;
366 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_VEC2:
367 return 72;
368 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_VEC3:
369 return 73;
370 case GL_UNSIGNED_INT_VEC4:
371 return 74;
372 case GL_SAMPLER_VIDEO_IMAGE_WEBGL:
373 return 75;
374 default:
375 UNREACHABLE();
376 return 0;
377 }
378}
379} // anonymous namespace
380
381const UniformTypeInfo &GetUniformTypeInfo(GLenum uniformType)
382{
383 ASSERT(kInfoTable[GetTypeInfoIndex(uniformType)].type == uniformType);
384 return kInfoTable[GetTypeInfoIndex(uniformType)];
385}
